{"tid":37273,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後會遇到更多的人？","createTime":"2016-12-13T09:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T13:30:08.000Z","uid":64840,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f58292a2475d5f41fc1df99baebaa8fd85540e54","tid":37273,"uid":64840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:02:04.000Z","msg":"你我分手的那天<br />\n<br />\n你説 「我不值得你這樣做」<br />\n你說 「我不配你待我這麼好」<br />\n你說 「以後的你會遇到更好的人」<br />\n<br />\n但其實我想說<br />\n你想分開的話 不妨直說<br />\n不用故意去貶低自己<br />\n更不用轉彎抹角去突顯我所謂的好<br />\n<br />\n因為分手從來只有一個原因<br />\n就是 愛不夠<br />\n何必找那麼多的藉口<br />\n那些通通都只是廢話<br />\n<br />\n「以後的你會遇到更好的人」<br />\n你是在說以後的你吧"},{"pid":"b3089716613c8e34ca6e467e95c8e907824d374b","tid":37273,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"好感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb36d6594bc5c598dff36f04bfbdaaffd87056a","tid":37273,"uid":1657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359f6db1a268f4cc45236243792dcabffbdd82a0","tid":37273,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"因為分手從來只有一個原因<br />\n就是 愛不夠<br />\n<br />\n唔好再沉醉係呢d傻尻說話度喇<br />\n祝你早d放低"},{"pid":"610a370eeed6481c529396782674301560ed9a14","tid":37273,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為分手從來只有一個原因<br />\n就是 愛不夠<br />\n<br />\n唔好再沉醉係呢d傻尻說話度喇<br />\n祝你早d放低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁仲有咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243dcb000f7ee4aa0b9e66fd263a6c8ca081daa2","tid":37273,"uid":61049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,